parserImport XOCL;

/******************************************************************************
 *                                                                            *
 *                   Flexible Generation of Text From Models                  *
 *                   ---------------------------------------                  *
 *                                                                            *
 *    Defines a construct that allows code (or more generally) text templates *
 *    to be defined where literal text can be interleaved with program code   *
 *    to generate output. The literal text and programs can be nested to any  *
 *    depth using a feature that is similar to [| with |] (lifting) and <     *
 *    with > (dropping) in abstract syntax.                                   *
 *                                                                            *
 ******************************************************************************/

context Root

  @Package CodeGen
  
    @Doc
      Defines a construct that allows code (or more generally) text templates 
      to be defined where literal text can be interleaved with program code   
      to generate output. The literal text and programs can be nested to any 
      depth using a feature that is similar to [| with |] (lifting) and <     
      with > (dropping) in abstract syntax.
    end
  
  end